There's a trail. We have her scent.

163
00:12:18,660 --> 00:12:21,500
我还以为这样的进展能激起你的斗志
I'd expected this development would encourage you.

164
00:12:22,080 --> 00:12:24,250
你的手下雷克托斯挑起争端
Was it for my encouragement that your man Rictus

165
00:12:24,250 --> 00:12:26,000
